Index.html:
The main HTML file that serves as the entry point for the app
SRC---Index.js: The JavaScript entry point where the DOM is rendered
SRC---App.js: The main component that serves as the root of the component tree 
SRC = We create components which we require


Components are the core building blocks of the react application
They help to create reusable block of code
IF anything goes wrong in the UI , It is very easy to find and solve it.
